# CODEOWNERS
# GitHub requires reviews from the matching owners below before a PR
# touching these paths can be merged (enable "Require review from Code
# Owners" in branch protection for this to take effect).
#
# Replace the team/usernames below with your actual GitHub teams.

# org-wide skills need 2 cross-functional approvers
/skills/org-wide/  @your-org/skills-review-board

# group skills need 1 approver from the owning group's lead team
/skills/group/     @your-org/group-leads

# project skills: owning team self-approves, no central review needed
/skills/project/   @your-org/skills-catalog-maintainers

# Catalog-level files (process changes) need the maintainers' sign-off
/CONTRIBUTING.md   @your-org/skills-catalog-maintainers
/CODEOWNERS        @your-org/skills-catalog-maintainers
